OL,7,FITV Wales has been contacted by
OL,8,Fserving officers at both North and
OL,9,FSouth Wales services who have
OL,10,Fexpressed their deep concern that Mr
OL,11,FMillington is not the right person to
OL,12,Ftake the service forward.
OL,14,FUnions have told ITV Wales, their
OL,15,Fmembers were "shocked" to learn of Mr
OL,16,FMillington's appointment. The is
OL,17,Fquestioning whether "due diligence"
OL,18,Fwas done and is calling into question
OL,19,Fwhether the process was "open and
OL,20,Ftransparent."
