OL,7,FEarlier this month, the took over
OL,8,Fresponsibility for South Wales Fire
OL,9,Fand Rescue Service after a exposed a
OL,10,Ftoxic culture in the service and the
OL,11,Fdeparture of its chief Huw Jakeway.
OL,13,FHannah Blythyn, the Deputy Minister
OL,14,Ffor Social Partnership, announced the
OL,15,Fappointment of four commissioners to
OL,16,Foversee reform. They include former
OL,17,FMinister for Education, Kirsty
OL,18,FWilliams, and former Chief Constable
OL,19,Fof North Wales Police, Carl Foulkes.
